        <Parent_String>money by function [300264714], money (objects) [300037316], exchange media (objects) [300387350], Exchange Media (hierarchy name) [300037221], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
